<!DOCTYPE html><html><head><title>$ command line ruby cheat sheets</title><link charset="utf-8" href="/style.css" media="screen" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /></head><body><div class="main"><div class="header"><h1><a href="/">cheat sheets.</a></h1><code class="header">$ command line ruby cheat sheets</code></div></div><div class="content"><pre>C-t c
	open xterm

C-t !
	run shell command

C-t w
	windows being managed
	
C-t n, C-t space, C-t enter
	next window
C-t p
	previous window
C-t d
	delete window
	
C-t s
	split window horizontally
C-t S
	split window vertically
C-t tab
	cycle through frames
C-t R
	remove frame
	
C-t r
	resize frame
C-p
	grow frame vertically
C-n
	shrink frame vertically
C-f
	grow frame horizontally
C-b
	shrink frame horizontally
return
	accept new frame size
C-g
	abort and restore frame to is original size</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
<a href="http://puma.io/">Puma</a> and, to a lesser extent,
<a href="http://errtheblog.com/">Err the Blog</a>.</div></body></html>